          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46851319/" class=" " title="sylviaswen">sylviaswen</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19917013">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">读小说的一个愿望：以读到某人的死来暖和自己寒颤的生命</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19917013/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-07-25 22:05</span>
                  
